"wiki":"<p>COMPONENTS:<br />\nCardboard:<br />\n1 Starting Player marker <br />\n1 Shortcut marker (with stand)<br />\n6 Shortcut tokens<br />\n1 Fennec marker (with stand)<br />\n6 Fennec tokens</p>\n\n<p>90 cards (56x82mm):<br />\n1 Shortcut card<br />\n1 Fennec card<br />\n30 Racing cards (6 in each Camel color - red, yellow, blue, green, purple): 5x with value 1, 1x with value 2. <br />\n5 Crazy Camel cards (black): 2x with 0, 2x with 1, 1x with 2. <br />\n12 Race Track cards (back = sandstorm)<br />\n1 Finish Line card<br />\n5 Leg Setup cards (1 per player count 2-6)<br />\n20 Leg Betting Winner cards (4 per Camel color): 2x with &pound;2 revenue, 1x with &pound;3 revenue, 1x with &pound;5 revenue)<br />\n5 Leg Betting Midfield cards (1 per Camel color)<br />\n5 Final Betting Overall Winner cards (1 per Camel color)<br />\n5 Final Betting Overall Loser cards (1 per Camel color)</p>\n\n<p>Plastic:<br />\n6 Racing Camels (36x25x15mm plastic)<br />\n80 Egyptian Coins: <br />\n50 value 1 (18mm dia. silver)<br />\n30 value 5 (22mm dia. gold)</p>\n\n<p>Rule booklet (12 p.).</p>\n\n","website":{"url":false},"imageid":"7288330","images":{"thumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/ucbPtg8yzolVPyeSPiXZ5A__small/img/M_uL5AxYNTZJ_Wk-XLs8nUklXFw=/fit-in/200x150/filters:strip_icc()/pic7288330.jpg","micro":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/ucbPtg8yzolVPyeSPiXZ5A__micro/img/ej5BQOKxF5CCys2YJuaO8dAUp14=/fit-in/64x64/filters:strip_icc()/pic7288330.jpg","square":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/ucbPtg8yzolVPyeSPiXZ5A__square/img/he5go4yR3r_1Htt1DyrAZfy2JVo=/75x75/filters:strip_icc()/pic7288330.jpg","tallthumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/ucbPtg8yzolVPyeSPiXZ5A__tallthumb/img/TtfTatuow69lMgG7Vfwb7qIEZI0=/fit-in/75x125/filters:strip_icc()/pic7288330.jpg","previewthumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/ucbPtg8yzolVPyeSPiXZ5A__previewthumb/img/RM5zbS3--6lccFXnx_ym062uZZ8=/fit-in/300x320/filters:strip_icc()/pic7288330.jpg","square200":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/ucbPtg8yzolVPyeSPiXZ5A__square20